%% MuGate — Sequence: Academic history sync
%% Source: HistoryController · HistoryService · PortalScraper.extractHistory
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant HistoryController
    participant HistoryService
    participant PortalScraper
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>HistoryController: POST /api/history/sync
    Note over HistoryController: authMiddleware · also triggered after login when stale
    HistoryController->>HistoryService: syncStudentHistoryFromPortal(userId)
    HistoryService->>DB: load + decrypt PortalCredentials
    HistoryService->>PortalScraper: extractHistory(credentials)
    PortalScraper->>PortalScraper: Playwright scrape MU portal
    PortalScraper-->>HistoryService: AcademicRecord[]
    HistoryService->>DB: txn upsert AcademicHistory and update GPA
    HistoryService-->>HistoryController: summary
    HistoryController-->>Client: 200
